name: Pak hic et nunc 1/6/2021
description: On Tuesday 1st June 2021 Pak returned to mint 99 editions for 999 Tezos each on hic et nunc. The fascinating part of this unannounced release was not the art work or how many collectors purchased, but the minting itself. This picture shows Pak is one of us by also experiencing backtracks when minting an objkt! So keep with it and don't be put off, this happens to the best of us. Shout out to _Fatberg_Slim and Hen House who noticed this activity immediately. Pak profile - https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/tz/tz1MBykkXwpvrFnk49bmf7VDRZrNyzxgUU4c Pak objkt - https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/109649
